{"id":374,"date":"2021-12-29T12:12:00","date_gmt":"2021-12-29T10:12:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/?p=374"},"modified":"2022-10-03T16:18:15","modified_gmt":"2022-10-03T13:18:15","slug":"blockchain-applications-in-cloud-banking","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/blockchain-applications-in-cloud-banking\/","title":{"rendered":"Blockchain applications in Cloud Banking Technologies"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The deployment of blockchain in <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/corporate-cloud-banking-and-strategic-growth\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"130\">cloud banking<\/a> provides untrusted parties with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbinsights.com\/research\/what-is-blockchain-technology\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">way to enter into an agreement<\/a> without relying on the services of a middleman.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>By providing a public ledger, cloud banking technologies using blockchain can provide a specific set of financial services, e.g., securitization or payments without requiring a bank.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, a <em>digital ledger provides<\/em> its users with additional tools such as self-executing contracts and smart contracts based on a digital ledger.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This cloud and data analytics <strong>Blockchain technology<\/strong> Impact of the blockchain technology platform is changing and distributing the contents of a will.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Distributed ledger technology (DLT), a \u2018cousin\u2019 to the blockchain, can help complete online payments requiring a high decentralization degree.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, many of these <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-multiple-payment-gateways-help-merchants-sell\/\" data-type=\"post\" data-id=\"182\">financial transactions<\/a> will need better coordination and may assist in establishing better governance and standards related to data sharing.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" wi